{"tid":59555,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有條物理想問","createTime":"2016-12-29T17:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T17:58:40.000Z","uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f25bf82e143f8451888676ef79c696d97075ad74","tid":59555,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNy2BXfPQykibpNJozTSzYYBQG5rLzuxTDsJJBafmB77k?filename=SXDmVe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXDmVe3.jpg&h=5cc48f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/013115_e5533327996d90a3f6fec654093d9b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F013115_e5533327996d90a3f6fec654093d9b39.jpg&h=1ef4469c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條題我唔係好識分入射角 仲有條虛線係應該點樣用<br />\n光一開始唔係由油90度入玻璃 點解冇發生全內反射仲入左去嘅?<br />\n希望各位可以教下小弟我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647b372e266895f273e131ba66f3d491ec065e5c","tid":59555,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:44:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76425c89c19ee00be6b20c62ed3da04e997f41ad","tid":59555,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3483c6075edd6edab21f8bfb207c320d56be319a","tid":59555,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNy2BXfPQykibpNJozTSzYYBQG5rLzuxTDsJJBafmB77k?filename=SXDmVe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXDmVe3.jpg&h=5cc48f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/013115_e5533327996d90a3f6fec654093d9b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F013115_e5533327996d90a3f6fec654093d9b39.jpg&h=1ef4469c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條題我唔係好識分入射角 仲有條虛線係應該點樣用<br />\n光一開始唔係由油90度入玻璃 點解冇發生全內反射仲入左去嘅?<br />\n希望各位可以教下小弟我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度有兩次折射<br />\n第一次，由空氣去玻璃，<br />\n第二次，由玻璃出番空氣<br />\n<br />\n謹記，所有角度都係由法線度起<br />\n法線係垂直個介質嘅相交面<br />\n<br />\n第一次折射<br />\n法線係垂直個面，所以係入射角係0，折射角都係0,<br />\n唔會有全內反射<br />\n況且，全內反射要係n大去n細(再加上入射角大於臨界角)先會有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由中心指出嘅虛線係第二次折射嘅法線"},{"pid":"6520490972937b83f77ad6df1eeb05f5f5b2177b","tid":59555,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:50:16.000Z","msg":"虛線係嗰個第二次折射嘅法線<br />\n入射角同反射角都係由虛線度起<br />\n<br />\n仲有可以用黎大概畫出嗰折射線出黎"},{"pid":"1dec1df57abb0047357b8552d5c324b28ca4cfca","tid":59555,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"入射線同法線嘅夾角就係入射角<br />\n折射線同法線嘅夾角就係折射角"},{"pid":"b0cb24b7359ff5710eaf5980a0f12deb904f4ba0","tid":59555,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:55:39.000Z","msg":"total internal reflection 要angle &gt; critical angle <br />\n而且由optically denser medium 去less dense 先會有<br />\n<br />\n入射角係講緊入去個點既normal同光線既角度 normal = 你條虛線<br />\n咁reflection angle 就睇你由咩medium 去邊到<br />\n會bend towards normal / away from normal"},{"pid":"20bdfd0d551bf7b1d898427cabb4ef83dfcd7e6f","tid":59555,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入射線同法線嘅夾角就係入射角<br />\n折射線同法線嘅夾角就係折射角</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明啦<br />\n同我諗嘅差唔多<br />\n個個真係計0度而唔係90度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5915878d7031886d3a545b13cbb2a7ef5b62210e","tid":59555,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>total internal reflection 要angle &amp;gt; critical angle <br />\n而且由optically denser medium 去less dense 先會有<br />\n<br />\n入射角係講緊入去個點既normal同光線既角度 normal = 你條虛線<br />\n咁reflection angle 就睇你由咩medium 去邊到<br />\n會bend towards normal / away from normal</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}